'''Golden Venture''' was a harvesting and exporting corporation on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]], their corporate headquarters based in [[Hedrett]]. Their goal was to harvest and export the wood from the local [[ch'hala tree]]s, but ran into resistance from the native [[Tarasin]]. The corporation went bankrupt when their plans failed.

